				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Toobin thinks out loud as he works in the security office. He's been tasked with updating the Steel Watcher's design, and locked in this room after his eyes were cut out. He's refused to give in to despair, however, and very much takes the NASA approach of 'work the problem'. "
